=I Want to be with You=

3
00:00:58,720 --> 00:01:01,180
=Yet Also Apart from You=

4
00:01:33,740 --> 00:01:35,180
When will you stop avoiding me?

5
00:01:39,260 --> 00:01:40,740
If I really wanted to avoid you,

6
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:43,820
