9
00:01:54,940 --> 00:01:56,020
Go back with me.

10
00:02:01,180 --> 00:02:02,300
Be good, alright?

11
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:17,660
You're joking.

12
00:02:22,340 --> 00:02:23,820
In a place like Lidu,

13
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:25,820
in front of so many people,

14
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:27,340
what danger could I possibly be in?

15
00:02:29,340 --> 00:02:31,220
Appearing as Wanwan

16
00:02:31,460 --> 00:02:32,860
is actually to protect myself.

17
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:35,100
Whether you're Wanwan

18
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,460
or Shen Zhiqiu,

19
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:41,580
you're leaving with me today.

20
00:02:47,780 --> 00:02:49,020
I'm a songstress,

21
00:02:50,180 --> 00:02:51,340
not a prostitute.

22
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:55,140
Don't worry.

23
00:03:01,860 --> 00:03:03,620
You're my fiancée.

24
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:04,900
How can I not worry about you?

25
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:07,540
Wanwan,

26
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:09,420
it's your turn on stage.

27
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:11,620
Why aren't you out yet?

28
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:13,220
Got it, Sister Hong.

29
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,780
I'm changing.

30
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:19,220
Third Master,

31
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:22,220
if you don't leave, people will...

32
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:27,780
You asked for an
extra performance yourself.

33
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:30,540
Why are you still dawdling back there?

34
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:41,100
Sister Hong,

35
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:42,620
I'm not done changing yet.

36
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:43,980
Please wait for me.

37
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:45,940
Sister Hong, someone's here to see you.

38
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:47,860
Coming.

39
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:49,740
Hurry up.

40
00:04:10,940 --> 00:04:12,340
People say that

41
00:04:12,580 --> 00:04:14,700
don't easily let others watch your back.

42
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:17,060
Third Master, you saw it.

43
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:19,100
I'm not carrying any weapons

44
00:04:19,340 --> 00:04:20,900
and won't assassinate

45
00:04:21,460 --> 00:04:22,740
your dear brother.

46
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:27,740
As long as you know

47
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:29,340
what you should and shouldn't do.

48
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:33,140
What should I do?

49
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:38,620
Live well.

50
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:54,700
Let me help you.

51
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:31,860
Third Master,

52
00:05:32,820 --> 00:05:33,900
