53
00:06:19,220 --> 00:06:20,060
How's it going?

54
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:23,220
She's right.

55
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,260
In a place like Lidu,

56
00:06:24,340 --> 00:06:25,780
if anything happens,

57
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:28,100
it'll be big news in Shen City.

58
00:06:29,140 --> 00:06:30,900
Yin Shixiong wouldn't dare act rashly.

59
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:34,620
I'll go check the West Warehouse.

60
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:35,860
You head back first.

61
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:37,860
